\cf2 \cb3 So do you think we now have everything in place to maximise BD and job placement opportunities to maximise commission, and we have left no stone unturned in terms of what claude can do to maximise the account director's financial potential\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
