\
The fourth is job-ad clustering on career pages and LinkedIn Jobs. Two or more mid-level IC/Corporate-Comms postings in a 30-day window on a single company's careers page are a leading indicator \
Landbase\
 of a Head-of hire within 60 days; either the new leader is already mid-hire and building a team, or the postings signal the incumbent's departure and a pending replacement search. Greenhouse, Workday and SmartRecruiters expose structured XML feeds; LinkedIn Jobs is scrapeable within ToS for public listings.\
